data.prayer: Jesus, you are the great high priest, please make the 24,925 believers in Östergötland, Sweden a worthy priesthood under you.
data.verse: Since then we have a great high priest who has passed through the heavens, Jesus, the Son of God, let us hold fast our confession.

data.location_label: Photo from the state of Östergötland, Sweden
data.section_summary: What conditions of religion or environment could you pray for here?

data.prayer: Father, help the 24,925 believers in Östergötland to know your commands and to do them.
data.verse: For Ezra had devoted himself to the study and observance of the Law of the Lord, and to teaching its decrees and laws in Israel.

data.prayer: Good Shepherd, thank you that you know the name of each of the 24,925 believers in Östergötland.
data.verse: I am the good shepherd; I know my sheep and my sheep know me

data.prayer: Father, help the stressed and anxious in Östergötland, Sweden know that you care for them today.
data.verse: Cast your cares on the Lord and he will sustain you; he will never let the righteous be shaken.

data.prayer: Lord, bring the blind by a way that they don’t know. Lead the Mandeaen people in paths that they don’t know. Make darkness light before them and crooked places straight. Do not forsake the Mandeaen people.
Spirit, renew the call of John the Baptist in the state of Östergötland. Send out bold servants who will call all to repent.
data.verse: Repent, for the kingdom of heaven is at hand.

data.prayer: Father, thank you that you will never abandon the church of Östergötland, Sweden.
data.verse: Be free from the love of money, content with such things as you have, for he has said, “I will in no way leave you, neither will I in any way forsake you.

data.prayer: Jesus, help the local leaders in Östergötland, Sweden not be proud but humble, and willing to wash the feet of all they serve.
data.verse: “You call me ‘Teacher’ and ‘Lord,’ and rightly so, for that is what I am. Now that I, your Lord and Teacher, have washed your feet, you also should wash one another’s feet. I have set you an example that you should do as I have done for you.
